snippet.title: Magic Assistant
snippet.description: Magic Assistant is multi-platform application for "Magic: The Gathering" players. Includes Card Browser, Library Organizer, Deck Builder and MTG Tournament Manager. Comes with MTG cards database and allows web updates. See home page for details.

snippet.title: Magic Set Editor Templates
snippet.description: This is a project dedicated to the creation and sharing of templates for the program Magic Set Editor (MSE).

snippet.title: Wizards Magic
snippet.description: Wizards Magic - OpenSource card game, based on rules of Magic: The Gathering, written in Python, using Pygame

snippet.title: CD+Graphics Magic
snippet.description: Timeline based editor for creating Compact Disc Subcode Graphics (also known as CD+G or CDG). Both karaoke and multimedia styles of content are supported. Please visit cdgmagic.sf.net for examples playable directly in the HTML5 CD+G player. CD+Graphics Scribe utility (separate download -- click "Browse All Files" above) can now convert existing CDG karaoke content to CMP (CD+Graphics Magic Project), LRC (Enhanced Lyrics), and ASS (Advanced SubStation Alpha) format.

snippet.title: hackxor
snippet.description: A webapp hacking game, where players must locate and exploit vulnerabilities to progress through the story. Think WebGoat but with a plot and a focus on realism&difficulty. Contains XSS, CSRF, SQLi, ReDoS, DOR, command injection, etc
